  "3255330": {
    "name": "Parasomnia: No REM",
    "steam_appid": 3255330,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255330/extras/363e477b03315e201661f772f47dfe9c.poster.avif?t=1769044838\" width=800 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255330/extras/363e477b03315e201661f772f47dfe9c.webm?t=1769044838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255330/extras/363e477b03315e201661f772f47dfe9c.mp4?t=1769044838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Parasomnia: No REM is a first-person psychological horror game that explores a new theme in the genre: <strong>sleepwalking</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game’s mechanics and environments adopt characteristics of this type of sleep disorder, offering both innovative and terrifying gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Connect with your sleepwalking body to interact between two worlds and discover the secrets your mind is trying to hide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255330/extras/1d0e2379be0bf74946a7ac88159607c2.webp?t=1769044838\" width=800 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 years have passed since the day your family disappeared. After several nights of insomnia, you decide to see a doctor for a solution. When you get home, you take sleeping pills to sleep better. However, they cause sleepwalking episodes that revive your childhood traumas, making sleep no longer a safe place…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255330/extras/4c252d6c68e9c0945dca475da1495c58.webp?t=1769044838\" width=800 height=26 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BETWEEN DREAMS AND NIGHTMARES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of someone suffering from sleepwalking episodes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a psychological horror experience where reality and dreams intertwine.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the unsettling No REM state, a point where the real world merges with the dream world, housing the protagonist's most macabre nightmares.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255330/extras/a867ee3e86858935c1848dcedb8440b3.poster.avif?t=1769044838\" width=800 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255330/extras/a867ee3e86858935c1848dcedb8440b3.webm?t=1769044838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255330/extras/a867ee3e86858935c1848dcedb8440b3.mp4?t=1769044838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>NOTHING IS AS IT SEEMS</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the world of dreams, the rules change completely! You won't be able to read, images will appear distorted, you have no control over your environment, and running is not an option…</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive entities that will try to approach you the moment you get distracted.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255330/extras/ecd82c5fd27d4476488229ed12c61684.poster.avif?t=1769044838\" width=800 height=355 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255330/extras/ecd82c5fd27d4476488229ed12c61684.webm?t=1769044838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> BRIDGE BETWEEN TWO WORLDS</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Connect with your sleepwalking body in the real world to interact with its objects.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255330/extras/006efa32c3cac7907f3356dfa0dcfcb0.poster.avif?t=1769044838\" width=800 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255330/extras/006efa32c3cac7907f3356dfa0dcfcb0.webm?t=1769044838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255330/extras/006efa32c3cac7907f3356dfa0dcfcb0.mp4?t=1769044838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SCARS FROM THE PAST</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delve deep into the unconscious to solve puzzles, combining the real world with the dream world to uncover the past that haunts you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255330/extras/cf89d87d5a7015de7623deb6d7c29013.poster.avif?t=1769044838\" width=800 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255330/extras/cf89d87d5a7015de7623deb6d7c29013.webm?t=1769044838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255330/extras/cf89d87d5a7015de7623deb6d7c29013.mp4?t=1769044838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
